[pybind11] Add synonyms that are forward-compatible with nanobind

These help ease Drake's transition to nanobind.
See https://github.com/RobotLocomotion/drake/issues/21572.

--- include/pybind11/attr.h
+++ include/pybind11/attr.h
@@ -118,6 +118,9 @@
 /// Annotation to mark enums as an arithmetic type
 struct arithmetic {};
 
+// Drake-specific forward-compatible synonym for nanobind.
+using is_arithmetic = arithmetic;
+
 /// Mark a function for addition at the beginning of the existing overload chain instead of the end
 struct prepend {};
 

